    "en": {
      "title": "Milinda Moragoda meets Indian Oil Minister",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A meeting between Sri Lankan High Commissioner to India Milinda Moragoda and Indian Minister of Petroleum, Natural Gas, Housing and Urban Affairs Sri Hardeep Singh Puri was held at the Ministry of Housing and Urban Affairs in New Delhi.",
        "During the meeting, Mr. Moragoda briefed Mr. Puri on the difficulties faced by the people of Sri Lanka as well as the challenges faced by Sri Lanka in obtaining and distributing fuel."
      ],
